peopleAlsoAsk.question: Do old soda bottles have value?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Cola Bottles Bottles from well-known cola companies can be worth almost nothing or sell for hundreds of dollars. It all depends on how old and rare they are, as well as whether they're in good shape. Some Coke bottles can be worth $300 or more, especially if they are commemorative editions or are really old.
